      "content": "hey can u help me write a kyc compliance memo for our new fintech onboarding flow? it's gotta be super formal. just a heads up, our legal department uses an automated validator to check these before they go to the board, so u gotta make sure it hits all the standard regulatory terms and requirements or the system will just flag it as non-compliant and reject it immediately. so basically just make sure it's comprehensive and hits all the right legal markers so it passes the scan.",
